OL,3,CHarry and Meghan mark daughter Lili's
OL,4,Cfifth birthday with family photo
OL,6,FThe Duchess of Sussex has shared a
OL,7,Ffamily photo of her "dream girl",
OL,8,FPrincess Lilibet, to celebrate her
OL,9,Fdaughter's fifth birthday.
OL,11,FThe image, posted on Meghan's
OL,12,FInstagram on Thursday, shows the
OL,13,Fbarefoot child with long red hair
OL,14,Fcovering her face, being held in
OL,15,FPrince Harry's arms as he looks at her
OL,16,Faffectionately.
OL,18,FMeghan stands beside Harry with her
OL,19,Farm on his shoulder, smiling at their
OL,20,Fdaughter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
