OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780617775
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan mark daughter Lili's
OL,4,Cfifth birthday with family photo
OL,6,FThe duchess wrote in the post: "Our
OL,7,Fdream girl. Happy 5th birthday, Lili",
OL,8,Ffollowed by a white heart emoji.
OL,10,FShe also shared another photo showing
OL,11,FLili standing barefoot on the grass in
OL,12,Fthe sunshine, wearing a summer dress.
OL,14,FLili is reaching out to touch the
OL,15,Fflowers of a blue-purple agapanthus,
OL,16,Fcommonly known as the Lily of the Nile
OL,17,For African Lily.
OL,19,FThe King's granddaughter was born on
OL,20,FJune 4 2021, in the US and named
OL,21,FLilibet Diana Mountbatten-Windsor.
