OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780617775
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan mark daughter Lili's
OL,4,Cfifth birthday with family photo
OL,6,FShe became entitled to use the title
OL,7,FPrincess only when King Charles
OL,8,Facceded to the throne, under rules set
OL,9,Fout by King George V in 1917.
OL,11,FPrince Harry and Meghan Markle began
OL,12,Fusing the titles Prince and Princess
OL,13,Ffor Archie and Lili after Lilibet's
OL,14,Fchristening in 2023, following
OL,15,Fcorrespondence with King Charles about
OL,16,Fthe matter.
OL,18,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,19,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,20,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,21,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
